## chart main Daily Parallel Agent Operating Story
```mermaid
flowchart LR
  intent["Operator intent\none clear request"]:::human
  entry{"Choose entry surface"}:::decision
  swimmers["Swimmers TUI or API\nrepo picker, batch, cockpit"]:::tool
  voice["Voice Entry\nmacOS dictation or iOS relay"]:::tool
  contract["Context Contract\nSkillbox focus + SBP cwd skills"]:::recommended
  fanout["One Prompt Fanout\nsame request, many cwd agents"]:::recommended
  fleet["Agent fleet\none tmux agent session per repo"]:::agent
  observe["Swimmers aquarium\nstate, terminal, diffs, skills, artifacts"]:::tool
  review["Review Loop\nattention, group input, evidence, closeout"]:::recommended
  example["Anonymized Example\nAPI + web + mobile release slice"]:::artifact

  intent --> entry
  entry -->|typed once| swimmers
  entry -->|spoken once| voice
  voice --> swimmers
  swimmers --> contract --> fanout --> fleet --> observe --> review
  example -. demonstrates .-> fanout

  classDef human fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0284c7,color:#0c4a6e,stroke-width:2px
  classDef tool fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b,color:#0f172a
  classDef agent fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f,stroke-width:2px
  classDef decision fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#3b0764,stroke-width:2px
  classDef recommended fill:#d1fae5,stroke:#059669,color:#064e3b,stroke-width:3px
  classDef artifact fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#6b7280,color:#111827
```

## chart fanout One Prompt Many CWD Launch Sequence
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant O as Operator
  participant S as Swimmers
  participant SBP as SBP
  participant A as Agent: repo A
  participant B as Agent: repo B
  participant C as Agent: repo C
  participant T as Tmux

  O->>S: Select repo A, repo B, repo C
  O->>S: Enter one initial request
  S->>SBP: Resolve cwd-scoped skills for each repo
  SBP-->>S: Skill visibility and prep receipts
  S->>T: Create batch with shared prompt excerpt
  par repo A
    T->>A: Start selected agent in cwd A
  and repo B
    T->>B: Start selected agent in cwd B
  and repo C
    T->>C: Start selected agent in cwd C
  end
  A-->>S: State, transcript, diff, artifacts
  B-->>S: State, transcript, diff, artifacts
  C-->>S: State, transcript, diff, artifacts
  O->>S: Send follow-up to ready sessions or inspect one cockpit
```

## chart context-contract Skillbox and SBP Context Contract
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  skillbox["Skillbox runtime graph\nrepos, services, skills, checks"]:::source
  focus["focus client/profile\nsync, bootstrap, up, collect, context"]:::process
  generated["Generated AGENTS/CLAUDE context\nwhat exists and how to operate it"]:::artifact
  sbp["SBP cwd read\nskills, MCP, beads, overlay state"]:::process
  prep{"Skill requested?"}:::decision
  activate["sbp skill activate --cwd\nrepo-local prep before launch"]:::recommended
  swimmers["Swimmers session skills panel\npassive cwd visibility"]:::tool
  prompt["Worker prompt\nselected_cwd, executor, matched skills, prep receipt"]:::artifact
  agent["Agent starts with explicit repo contract"]:::agent

  skillbox --> focus --> generated --> sbp --> prep
  prep -->|yes| activate --> prompt
  prep -->|no| prompt
  sbp --> swimmers
  prompt --> agent

  classDef source fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0284c7,color:#0c4a6e,stroke-width:2px
  classDef process fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#64748b,color:#0f172a
  classDef decision fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#3b0764,stroke-width:2px
  classDef recommended fill:#d1fae5,stroke:#059669,color:#064e3b,stroke-width:3px
  classDef artifact fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#6b7280,color:#111827
  classDef tool fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f,stroke-width:2px
  classDef agent fill:#dcfce7,stroke:#16a34a,color:#14532d,stroke-width:2px
```

## chart voice-entry Voice and Mobile Entry Path
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant H as Human
  participant Mac as voice-to-text
  participant IOS as vtt-ios
  participant Relay as Trusted relay
  participant Router as cwd router
  participant SBP as SBP prep
  participant S as Swimmers

  alt macOS dispatch mode
    H->>Mac: Speak task once
    Mac->>Router: Clean transcript and choose cwd
  else iOS foreground note
    H->>IOS: Record one voice note
    IOS->>Relay: Upload audio with pairing token
    Relay->>Router: Transcribe, clean, route
  end
  Router->>SBP: Activate requested skills for selected cwd
  SBP-->>Router: Prep receipt
  Router->>S: POST hidden session with worker prompt
  S-->>H: Session appears in aquarium with status and artifacts
```

## chart example Anonymized Parallel Agent Example
```mermaid
flowchart TD
  brief["Example prompt\nMake the beta release path real across API, web, mobile, and docs"]:::human
  pick["Pick cwd set\nrepo-api, repo-web, repo-ios, repo-docs"]:::decision
  batch["Swimmers batch\nsame mission, per-cwd execution"]:::recommended

  api["repo-api agent\nrelay contract and server checks"]:::agent
  web["repo-web agent\noperator cockpit and proof UI"]:::agent
  ios["repo-ios agent\nclient smoke and redaction gates"]:::agent
  docs["repo-docs agent\nrunbook and evidence worksheet"]:::agent

  evidence["Shared evidence packet\ncommands, screenshots, logs, blocked gates"]:::artifact
  merge{"Coordinator review"}:::decision
  follow["Group follow-up\nsame correction to ready sessions"]:::recommended
  close["Closeout\nbeads synced, tests named, residual risk explicit"]:::artifact

  brief --> pick --> batch
  batch --> api --> evidence
  batch --> web --> evidence
  batch --> ios --> evidence
  batch --> docs --> evidence
  evidence --> merge
  merge -->|needs correction| follow --> api
  merge -->|accepted| close

  classDef human fill:#e0f2fe,stroke:#0284c7,color:#0c4a6e,stroke-width:2px
  classDef decision fill:#ede9fe,stroke:#7c3aed,color:#3b0764,stroke-width:2px
  classDef recommended fill:#d1fae5,stroke:#059669,color:#064e3b,stroke-width:3px
  classDef agent fill:#fef3c7,stroke:#d97706,color:#78350f,stroke-width:2px
  classDef artifact fill:#f3f4f6,stroke:#6b7280,color:#111827
```

## chart review-loop Monitor Steer Verify Close
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Launched
  Launched --> Working: agent reads repo contract
  Working --> Waiting: needs operator input
  Working --> EvidenceReady: tests or proof produced
  Waiting --> Steered: targeted input or batch group input
  Steered --> Working
  EvidenceReady --> Review: inspect diff, transcript, artifacts
  Review --> Working: issue found
  Review --> Verified: commands and proof pass
  Verified --> Closed: bead or task closed and synced
  Closed --> [*]

  state Waiting {
    [*] --> Attention
    Attention --> LaunchNext: optional next prompt in same cwd
    LaunchNext --> [*]
  }
```
